{"tid":2367760,"cid":12,"subCid":0,"title":"一件發生喺你身上巧合到冇人會信嘅事","createTime":"2021-01-15T15:11:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-15T22:06:13.000Z","uid":218994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"636a3db2b263f65aa8c0fd661cf1334fe2b68b11","tid":2367760,"uid":218994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:11:17.000Z","msg":"當年仲讀緊書<br />\n每個sem 都同啲frd 夾埋一齊add 科<br />\n有次add/drop period 我係咁提個frd add 一科（core嚟，一定要take)<br />\n因為就冇位，add唔到佢就會遲一年先grad <br />\n但佢唔嗲唔吊咁又冇乜覆<br />\n到咗deadline嗰日佢話返屋企先搞啦<br />\n當晚11:59pm就截止<br />\n咁我就算啦理唔到佢咁多<br />\n<br />\n點知嗰晚我喺銅鑼灣11:45pm左右搭MTR<br />\n喺閘口撞到佢<br />\n我即刻問佢add 咗未<br />\n佢話未喎<br />\n於是我即刻唔俾佢出閘<br />\n咁啱後面就係當時地鐵站俾人上網啲電腦<br />\n即刻趕到截止前5分鐘add科<br />\n我同佢完全冇約過"},{"pid":"8d090acbbf703a152f94332752c21339e3745aab","tid":2367760,"uid":200405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"你咁好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個frd要defer足一年都唔理都犀利"},{"pid":"a9f20bf4131f0e0041b9359fcec9d8da9f971b1b","tid":2367760,"uid":218994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d090acbbf703a152f94332752c21339e3745aab","tid":2367760,"uid":200405,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:13:44.000Z","msg":"你咁好心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你個frd要defer足一年都唔理都犀利"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T15:15:10.000Z","msg":"咁都想一齊grad嘅<br />\n佢嘅性格係咁<br />\n之後佢出嚟做嘢都係抖夠先揾工咁<br />\n好似揾咗一年都冇做嘢"},{"pid":"1091db0cb650be0d03405ffe38a177275ce67c45","tid":2367760,"uid":176592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-15T22:06:13.000Z","msg":"講故台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}